<body>
    <h1>RQ005 - Permitir Rastreabilidade entre Planos de A=C3=A7=C3=A3o</h1=
>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-m=
acro-note">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-info=
rmation-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p local-id=3D"bf5538c85070"><strong>Obs: Validar o nome com a Equipe do Pr=
oduto e Ux Design</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"9a062bbd843d"><strong>=E2=80=9CPlanos Correlacionados=E2=80=
=9D ou =E2=80=9CPlanos Relacionados=E2=80=9D ou =E2=80=9CPlanos Vinculados=
=E2=80=9D ?</strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"0c41c4bbfc13"></p>
<h1 local-id=3D"926d9908816e" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-1.Contexto">1. Contexto</h1>
<p local-id=3D"87ca23afdb60">Implementa=C3=A7=C3=A3o da capacidade de relac=
ionar livremente Planos de A=C3=A7=C3=A3o entre si, estabelecendo uma conex=
=C3=A3o sem=C3=A2ntica e bidirecional.</p>
<p local-id=3D"733abf6c5b37">Essa funcionalidade permite que os usu=C3=A1ri=
os identifiquem planos que possuem sinergia, depend=C3=AAncias informais ou=
 temas em comum, facilitando a navega=C3=A7=C3=A3o e a vis=C3=A3o integrada=
 da opera=C3=A7=C3=A3o, sem impor uma hierarquia ou rela=C3=A7=C3=A3o de pr=
eced=C3=AAncia entre os planos.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"fa00e065-61d7-405c-8f11-8a9c7af23c4b">
<h1 local-id=3D"4c49c3a10c95" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-2.RequisitosFuncionais(RF)">2. Requisitos Funcionais (RF)=
</h1>
<h3 local-id=3D"855338bc37b5" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-RF001=E2=80=93Associa=C3=A7=C3=A3oBidirecionalN:N">RF001 =
=E2=80=93 Associa=C3=A7=C3=A3o Bidirecional N:N</h3>
<p local-id=3D"c0b6fd579ded">O sistema deve permitir que um Plano de A=C3=
=A7=C3=A3o seja vinculado a m=C3=BAltiplos outros planos.</p>
<p local-id=3D"990b4addc4a2">Ao associar o Plano A ao Plano B, o Plano B de=
ver=C3=A1 exibir automaticamente o Plano A como plano correlato, garantindo=
 uma rela=C3=A7=C3=A3o bidirecional autom=C3=A1tica.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"46cc9d9557e9">
<li local-id=3D"c83f2075640f">
<p local-id=3D"4d8db05a71bd">Os planos de a=C3=A7=C3=A3o dispon=C3=ADveis p=
ara v=C3=ADnculo ser=C3=A3o <strong>exclusivamente os planos de a=C3=A7=C3=
=A3o de =C3=A1rea</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d05c7b970615">
<p local-id=3D"a1676fff3a9a">A funcionalidade de vincular estar=C3=A1 dispo=
n=C3=ADvel <strong>somente no m=C3=B3dulo de Plano de A=C3=A7=C3=A3o do Pla=
no Estrat=C3=A9gico</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"71784d153ef1">
<p local-id=3D"1081e4f62ff6">A vincula=C3=A7=C3=A3o entre planos n=C3=A3o f=
ormar=C3=A3o estruturas hier=C3=A1rquicas ou em =C3=A1rvore. O relacionamen=
to ser=C3=A1 sempre direto entre<strong> origem e destino</strong>, sem pro=
paga=C3=A7=C3=A3o em cadeia.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"1a7d1f03ecd6" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">Exemplo: ao vin=
cular o Plano A ao Plano B, e o Plano B ao Plano C, o Plano A exibir=C3=A1 =
apenas o Plano B como correlato, n=C3=A3o sendo exibido o Plano C.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"6e95a9927896">
<li local-id=3D"ff9d7af049af">
<p local-id=3D"1589afc23847">Regras de acesso entre Planos vinculados: O v=
=C3=ADnculo entre planos n=C3=A3o altera permiss=C3=B5es de acesso. Ou seja=
: Usu=C3=A1rios do Plano A n=C3=A3o ter=C3=A3o acesso autom=C3=A1tico ao Pl=
ano B; O acesso continuar=C3=A1 respeitando as regras atuais (=C3=A0rea) do=
 sistema.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"165bb3d1-c8c1-4360-9eaf-9a509a4189f3">
<h3 local-id=3D"33ab2877b6c0" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-RF002=E2=80=93InterfacedeGerenciamentodeCorrelatos">RF002=
 =E2=80=93 Interface de Gerenciamento de Correlatos</h3>
<p local-id=3D"a1e1fdb04a0e">O sistema dever=C3=A1 disponibilizar uma inter=
face para gerenciamento das vincula=C3=A7=C3=A3o contendo:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"8d257669-4634-42cb-94bd-5e2d4c1fb25e">
<li local-id=3D"4bf1253d-dee7-44c1-82b2-cc7ad05a5f67">
<p local-id=3D"49c93e2a7056">Componente de busca de planos de a=C3=A7=C3=A3=
o</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"69d1749e-7b82-4c24-b06b-6ed0528ef669">
<p local-id=3D"6a1f63fdf1ad">Selecionar m=C3=BAltiplos planos de a=C3=A7=C3=
=A3o</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fbf220d1-1525-4fb4-87de-f009d17ec552">
<p local-id=3D"58f9d6bec903">A=C3=A7=C3=B5es para adicionar ou remover corr=
ela=C3=A7=C3=B5es</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"03c3a5682fcd">A sele=C3=A7=C3=A3o dever=C3=A1 ocorrer por me=
io de modal</p>
<hr local-id=3D"ee8fd89d42c3">
<h3 local-id=3D"0c045761bb6d" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-RF003=E2=80=93MotordeBuscaeFiltragem">RF003 =E2=80=93 Mot=
or de Busca e Filtragem</h3>
<p local-id=3D"147a20d33abc">O sistema dever=C3=A1 permitir localizar plano=
s candidatos =C3=A0 vincula=C3=A7=C3=A3o atrav=C3=A9s de:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"7ff30d1f-b59e-4674-912d-8daebc50dc4a">
<li local-id=3D"5afb434f-c31b-42c6-961a-2cc7e94ca2f3">
<p local-id=3D"cb246460b50d">t=C3=ADtulo do plano</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"65338832-d247-4032-9eaa-40ef8b6f5d20">
<p local-id=3D"667d92eea65b">c=C3=B3digo do plano</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1f153ba0-dbe6-4aac-ab6d-f4d0287788c4">
<p local-id=3D"18cdf2f028d1">status</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"df99441a-88f0-4966-a490-453b27d997bf">
<p local-id=3D"3ca461b23af5">respons=C3=A1vel</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"77877122-56e8-454d-aea0-df4f780a3343">
<p local-id=3D"47448c13bc78">=C3=A1rea</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"18f9fe37-eea1-435e-a162-28a9dceffc84">
<p local-id=3D"ec1c40eb9575">tags</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"38ffc93c-05c5-43d6-b9ce-5636425d65e4">
<p local-id=3D"3714dbf94952">per=C3=ADodo</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"cf362fc7-f4df-4df2-9fda-7efdaab3ea30">
<h3 local-id=3D"7047000d97e7" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-RF004=E2=80=93Visualiza=C3=A7=C3=A3odePlanosVinculados">R=
F004 =E2=80=93 Visualiza=C3=A7=C3=A3o de Planos Vinculados</h3>
<p local-id=3D"00d7dd7139e8">Os planos vinculados dever=C3=A3o ser exibidos=
 na tela de detalhamento do Plano de A=C3=A7=C3=A3o.</p>
<p local-id=3D"1e1cea007b2f">A visualiza=C3=A7=C3=A3o poder=C3=A1 ocorrer e=
m formato de:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c637368e-0042-4d7b-a65e-084c25bb4c36">
<li local-id=3D"9233625b-e3b2-4edf-9a77-05d39515b5f5">
<p local-id=3D"55e0c9a6045d"><strong>Cards/Chips </strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b6366702-2daf-42ab-ae6d-57bc658cd4a2">
<p local-id=3D"1ba165bd202a"><strong>Lista compacta</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"cf677239251f">Cada item dever=C3=A1 permitir:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"7004b2f9-290d-468b-8942-923acb975b41">
<li local-id=3D"c15b46d8-d56f-429a-90fa-e6f3b262f4eb">
<p local-id=3D"544d65956c9c"><strong>abrir o plano correlato </strong></p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"b327b95c-8cef-4487-9eba-e56de5827e4d">
<p local-id=3D"56b93253d2d2"><strong>remover o v=C3=ADnculo (apenas o Gesto=
r do Plano de a=C3=A7=C3=A3o de origem)</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"ca47f2a6-36e2-43f7-9056-1af917dd4d8c">
<h3 local-id=3D"e39ed92cc00b" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-RF005=E2=80=93SistemadeNotifica=C3=A7=C3=B5es(poremail)">=
RF005 =E2=80=93 Sistema de Notifica=C3=A7=C3=B5es (por email)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"108197fadc4a">O sistema dever=C3=A1 notificar por email os <=
strong>respons=C3=A1veis pelos planos envolvidos (gestor do plano de a=C3=
=A7=C3=A3o)</strong> quando:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"f6f5c747-5c24-4f7a-8152-6efd188d0cba">
<li local-id=3D"68e036e7-dbc0-4327-a310-32c0b15b26c1">
<p local-id=3D"1d52c2aae25f">uma nova vincula=C3=A7=C3=A3o for criada</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"1cc54e78-74c2-4607-9f50-3364568e701c">
<p local-id=3D"28681b5c14e1">uma vincula=C3=A7=C3=A3o for removida</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4470892b2014">A notifica=C3=A7=C3=A3o dever=C3=A1 informar:<=
/p>
<ul local-id=3D"69f6610e-4fe1-48c3-9718-e6a72ab1ac69">
<li local-id=3D"39c4e56f-5e2c-4b2f-bd8e-f66eb1c0011e">
<p local-id=3D"c8308b81e995">plano relacionado</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"552ba1a3-2ff1-48b3-b602-b1f1d220edfd">
<p local-id=3D"f202c399a9d7">usu=C3=A1rio respons=C3=A1vel pela a=C3=A7=C3=
=A3o</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"368bbe2d-cdda-448e-a72e-f5d316165e91">
<p local-id=3D"7e77ef285d7a">data e hora da a=C3=A7=C3=A3o</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"2feaaf88-22f9-47a0-953d-d648b98148ef">
<h1 local-id=3D"872ab9a59bad" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-3.RegrasdeNeg=C3=B3cio(RN)">3. Regras de Neg=C3=B3cio (RN=
)</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"da5eaa92ab38" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-RelacionadasaoRF001eRF002">Relacionadas ao RF001 e RF002<=
/h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"c8a7ac946a29" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-RN001=E2=80=93ImpedimentodeAutoassocia=C3=A7=C3=A3o">RN00=
1 =E2=80=93 Impedimento de Autoassocia=C3=A7=C3=A3o</h3>
<p local-id=3D"ad7b6ab7a96b">O sistema deve impedir que um Plano de A=C3=A7=
=C3=A3o seja associado a ele mesmo. N=C3=A3o deve ser listado.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"40ad0bb4-9c72-4d69-9f05-31bfe34abe9f">
<h3 local-id=3D"9adf5dcc5c11" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-RN002=E2=80=93Preven=C3=A7=C3=A3odeDuplicidade">RN002 =E2=
=80=93 Preven=C3=A7=C3=A3o de Duplicidade</h3>
<p local-id=3D"3f1ee96f8ef2">O sistema n=C3=A3o deve permitir a cria=C3=A7=
=C3=A3o de mais de um v=C3=ADnculo entre o mesmo par de planos.<br>
Ex: n=C3=A3o ser=C3=A1 permitido ter a correla=C3=A7=C3=A3o da seguinte for=
ma:<br><br>
A (origem) =E2=86=92 B (destino) e B (origem) =E2=86=92 A (destino)</p>
<hr local-id=3D"6e12ec89-a0d3-4387-9668-6b59782bce34">
<h3 local-id=3D"00d63ced49b4" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-RN003=E2=80=93AtomicidadedaRela=C3=A7=C3=A3o">RN003 =E2=
=80=93 Atomicidade da Rela=C3=A7=C3=A3o</h3>
<p local-id=3D"ac445a9b08ae">A cria=C3=A7=C3=A3o ou exclus=C3=A3o da correl=
a=C3=A7=C3=A3o deve ocorrer <strong>de forma transacional</strong>, garanti=
ndo que o v=C3=ADnculo seja refletido simultaneamente em ambos os planos vi=
nculados.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"e7c1e947-69d9-4434-9f78-376dfdc3969a">
<h2 local-id=3D"0cb0fc5ae025" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-RelacionadasaoRF003eRF004">Relacionadas ao RF003 e RF004<=
/h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"160574863d2d" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-RN004=E2=80=93VisibilidadeporPermiss=C3=A3o">RN004 =E2=80=
=93 Visibilidade por Permiss=C3=A3o</h3>
<p local-id=3D"e65ecceca734">Na busca por planos vinculados, o usu=C3=A1rio=
 s=C3=B3 poder=C3=A1 visualizar e selecionar planos aos quais ele possui, n=
o m=C3=ADnimo, permiss=C3=A3o de leitura.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"8bb6b30d-489a-47e7-8ee6-b47c8c76c86d">
<h3 local-id=3D"4403a3ee785e" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-RN005=E2=80=93Restri=C3=A7=C3=A3oparaPlanosFinalizados">R=
N005 =E2=80=93 Restri=C3=A7=C3=A3o para Planos Finalizados</h3>
<p local-id=3D"92d7df65074d">Planos Finalizados mant=C3=AAm seus v=C3=ADncu=
los existentes, mas n=C3=A3o podem receber novas correla=C3=A7=C3=B5es a me=
nos que o usu=C3=A1rio tenha permiss=C3=A3o administrativa.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"8c5c1e15-0d8f-4065-83a9-eed8a2c99a27">
<h2 local-id=3D"7e16363cf2d3" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-RelacionadasaoRF005">Relacionadas ao RF005</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"82bf5b8658ee" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-RN006=E2=80=93Permiss=C3=A3odeEdi=C3=A7=C3=A3o">RN006 =E2=
=80=93 Permiss=C3=A3o de Edi=C3=A7=C3=A3o</h3>
<p local-id=3D"c269cdc99c9d">Apenas usu=C3=A1rios com permiss=C3=A3o de edi=
=C3=A7=C3=A3o no plano "origem" podem adicionar ou remover correla=C3=A7=C3=
=B5es. (Gestor do plano de a=C3=A7=C3=A3o)<br></p>
<hr local-id=3D"f7980243-3227-4b3d-9866-6427c8f78179">
<h1 local-id=3D"8da0317e87af" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-4.PremissasGerais">4. Premissas Gerais</h1>
<ul local-id=3D"421ad5b4-ab32-4df2-9809-e93c7a405711">
<li local-id=3D"9d22e622-6470-4e63-98f8-91057329668f">
<p local-id=3D"2f9adbc3bf03">A correla=C3=A7=C3=A3o possui <strong>car=C3=
=A1ter exclusivamente informativo</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c068d8a8-af97-47db-a2fb-b0356dabb4de">
<p local-id=3D"8c69282184df">N=C3=A3o haver=C3=A1:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e956ba7b-3077-4e44-82da-9c7b2973d34c">
<li local-id=3D"018fad3e-ad8c-4d3c-8e6f-1afdebd1bec0">
<p local-id=3D"320e93ee623b">heran=C3=A7a de prazos</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"16227063-2b24-40d8-9c81-62262dca0b7a">
<p local-id=3D"46866d2d39df">depend=C3=AAncia de execu=C3=A7=C3=A3o</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"e7506cf9-a781-455e-9d92-c71c0bf3df11">
<p local-id=3D"f963e17e08a2">impacto em c=C3=A1lculos de progresso</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"35fab4ee-9b8b-4c5e-9a0a-3bd7eaac8895">
<p local-id=3D"09664223ce38">bloqueios operacionais.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"239c7c7f-8b12-42af-8048-536b4adbf65d">
<p local-id=3D"035bfd71179d">A exclus=C3=A3o l=C3=B3gica de um Plano de A=
=C3=A7=C3=A3o dever=C3=A1 remover automaticamente suas refer=C3=AAncias (or=
igem e destino) na tabela de correla=C3=A7=C3=B5es.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"81ca2ba5-54bb-4610-9fca-d6c916c31fec">
<p local-id=3D"3e74aa44feb8">A interface dever=C3=A1 suportar <strong>lista=
s extensas de correlatos</strong>, utilizando:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b48a1e09-3f2b-4b77-a677-d67cb10c62e0">
<li local-id=3D"f8c51672-82e6-4960-95a1-5792743ca4cf">
<p local-id=3D"79e5b6cbcda5">pagina=C3=A7=C3=A3o</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e9ba9d72-f560-4170-9857-03c4aa87ec21">
<p local-id=3D"8cf9186e6f46">carregamento sob demanda</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"8b4080fdbfbf">
<h1 local-id=3D"02b603d56554" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-5.Est=C3=B3riasdoUsu=C3=A1rio(UserStories)"><strong>5. Es=
t=C3=B3rias do Usu=C3=A1rio (User Stories)</strong></h1>
<ul local-id=3D"b58ec7b6-bf76-40a6-b457-4500942bbc43">
<li local-id=3D"85d1eb95-3303-47c0-ac92-576c7f3ef289">
<p local-id=3D"eec1c1d427b0"><strong>Eu como</strong> Gestor de Projeto, <s=
trong>quero</strong> relacionar meu plano de a=C3=A7=C3=A3o ao plano de out=
ro departamento que trata de um tema similar, <strong>para que</strong> pos=
samos trocar boas pr=C3=A1ticas e evitar a=C3=A7=C3=B5es redundantes.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"14dbb33d-1081-4e5b-950e-53ad2340889c">
<li local-id=3D"421bce52-8ada-4d93-ba92-190f12804c6c">
<p local-id=3D"2df26bf33d7e"><em>Crit=C3=A9rios de Aceite:</em> O v=C3=ADnc=
ulo deve ser vis=C3=ADvel para ambos os gestores; Deve ser poss=C3=ADvel cl=
icar no plano correlato e ser redirecionado para ele.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"0b09aac2-c7f3-4b7a-a6d3-af2e59223a85">
<p local-id=3D"84be720d5084"><strong>Eu como</strong> Analista de Opera=C3=
=A7=C3=B5es, <strong>quero</strong> filtrar os planos por "=C3=81rea" e "Ta=
gs" ao buscar um correlato, <strong>para que</strong> eu encontre rapidamen=
te o plano espec=C3=ADfico em uma base com milhares de registros.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"0b624b98-baf7-4bf7-8c5b-5364a286a918">
<li local-id=3D"4b1a7759-1557-4dc1-a91f-e2c26988132d">
<p local-id=3D"ef5531fa1d61"><em>Crit=C3=A9rios de Aceite:</em> Os filtros =
devem ser cumulativos; A busca deve retornar resultados em tempo real ou co=
m lat=C3=AAncia m=C3=ADnima.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"d702fad6-74dd-478d-aab9-04fe3aa04e2b">
<p local-id=3D"e0b37c3f074a"><strong>Eu como</strong> Respons=C3=A1vel por =
um Plano, <strong>quero</strong> receber um aviso quando algu=C3=A9m correl=
acionar o plano de outra =C3=A1rea ao meu, <strong>para que</strong> eu tom=
e ci=C3=AAncia de que meu trabalho est=C3=A1 sendo usado como refer=C3=AAnc=
ia ou possui depend=C3=AAncia externa.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"863c7c48-9b71-482c-b3c8-c576c1e67a79">
<li local-id=3D"fe94a879-28c4-44ca-8018-601c0cb00a8d">
<p local-id=3D"e485fdec0f6f"><em>Crit=C3=A9rios de Aceite:</em> A notifica=
=C3=A7=C3=A3o deve conter o nome do plano correlacionado e quem realizou a =
a=C3=A7=C3=A3o.</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"62874961c74c">
<h1 local-id=3D"a9297d62796c" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-6.Orienta=C3=A7=C3=B5esparaDesigndaInterface">6. Orienta=
=C3=A7=C3=B5es para Design da Interface</h1>
<p local-id=3D"42eb6d4e97f0"></p>
<p local-id=3D"db252d56943f"><img src=3D"https://channel.atlassian.net/wiki=
/plugins/servlet/confluence/placeholder/error?i18nKey=3Deditor.placeholder.=
error&amp;locale=3Dpt_BR&amp;version=3D2" title=3D"Cannot invoke &quot;Stri=
ng.indexOf(int)&quot; because &quot;href&quot; is null" class=3D"transform-=
error" data-encoded-xml=3D"%3Cac%3Aemoticon+ac%3Aname%3D%22location%22+ac%3=
Aemoji-shortname%3D%22%3Around_pushpin%3A%22+ac%3Aemoji-id%3D%221f4cd%22+ac=
%3Alocal-id%3D%22705d52326eb1%22+ac%3Aemoji-fallback%3D%22%F0%9F%93%8D%22+%=
2F%3E"> <strong>Local: </strong>Menu do Plano estrat=C3=A9gico -&gt; Plano =
de a=C3=A7=C3=A3o =E2=86=92 icone para planos =E2=80=9Ccorrelacionados=E2=
=80=9D<br><br>
Criar um icone na op=C3=A7=C3=A3o de ferramentas para que seja direcionada =
a nova tela de planos de a=C3=A7=C3=A3o vinculados.<br></p><span class=3D"c=
onfluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-ma=
nual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"ima=
ge-20260316-152758.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"78f1a56761ba3=
a76ca8527a226219f7bcda9f5418c019b388e1bdb5e6d668735" data-image-src=3D"http=
s://channel.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/4081614853/image-202603=
16-152758.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1773674882636&amp;cacheVer=
sion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"734" data-width=3D"1702" data-unresol=
ved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"4093050881" data-linked-=
resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked=
-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260316-152758.png" data-base-url=3D"http=
s://channel.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/=
png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"4081614853" data-linked-resource-=
container-version=3D"11" data-media-id=3D"f061bca9-3269-4c80-8f20-1f60f8874=
6e9" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"201"></span>
<p local-id=3D"eb055b65d2d8"><br>
Tela: Correla=C3=A7=C3=A3o entre Planos de A=C3=A7=C3=A3o</p>
<p local-id=3D"7c0d24a8f596">O designer dever=C3=A1 projetar os componentes=
 de interface que permitam <strong>visualizar, adicionar e remover correla=
=C3=A7=C3=B5es entre Planos de A=C3=A7=C3=A3o</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"6bd74504e779">A proposta de layout deve contemplar os seguin=
tes elementos:</p>
<hr local-id=3D"cb30705a-0cbe-44f3-ad1c-a98029662dbd">
<h2 local-id=3D"14004bb266f1" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-Visualiza=C3=A7=C3=A3odePlanosCorrelatos">Visualiza=C3=A7=
=C3=A3o de Planos Correlatos</h2>
<p local-id=3D"ddb5dfe94a88">Na <strong>tela de detalhamento do Plano de A=
=C3=A7=C3=A3o</strong>, deve existir uma se=C3=A7=C3=A3o chamada:</p>
<p local-id=3D"4f1fdf338a56"><strong><span style=3D"background-color: rgb(2=
48,230,160);">=E2=80=9CPlanos Correlacionados=E2=80=9D ou =E2=80=9CPlanos R=
elacionados=E2=80=9D ?</span></strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"9af73a91d715">Essa se=C3=A7=C3=A3o deve apresentar:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"fca5c6f6-acd2-4905-a99a-6f31aef8f818">
<li local-id=3D"fccbffee-8cf4-4842-8f51-847b4e344e5f">
<p local-id=3D"deda47e9c388">Lista de <strong>planos correlacionados ao pla=
no atual</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d1c889ef-7713-4433-aab6-4b8ca97759ef">
<p local-id=3D"94aaf747c791">Visualiza=C3=A7=C3=A3o em formato de:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"2cf14479-46de-439a-98fe-116c4e7ab3f9">
<li local-id=3D"662a5983-358a-42fd-9015-1a7766b0ae8e">
<p local-id=3D"3414146dfe9d"><strong>cards/chips</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dfcd6893-8929-4a81-a85c-c7a5d9392c7d">
<p local-id=3D"7202c5b435fd"><strong>lista compacta</strong></p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4c5008b1e0c7">Cada item dever=C3=A1 apresentar:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a1ebe660-4d53-4a3e-a1e0-97691539939a">
<li local-id=3D"e1197d08-34b5-4b9c-b689-d49219072857">
<p local-id=3D"41215e06fc5b">Nome do plano</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"74c497cd-3feb-4f9f-96c0-dcf3c293f6e2">
<p local-id=3D"f39aaef226db">C=C3=B3digo do plano</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"75367040-1dd4-49a8-8d52-a0fd9072f3b3">
<p local-id=3D"18b7b2ad2701">Status do plano</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8f32c6418517">
<p local-id=3D"27d93a776563">Gr=C3=A1fico com andamento das a=C3=A7=C3=B5es=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"21a9d3f6346a">
<p local-id=3D"487954eae715">Data limite do plano de a=C3=A7=C3=A3o</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"b329a78f-e676-42ef-b371-a5d494982a47">
<p local-id=3D"5b9070963e70">A=C3=A7=C3=A3o para <strong>abrir o plano</str=
ong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"46e544f1-7acd-46f2-a7eb-13792e0f9d6e">
<p local-id=3D"a3285cfaaac0">A=C3=A7=C3=A3o para <strong>remover a correla=
=C3=A7=C3=A3o (para o plano de a=C3=A7=C3=A3o de origem que estiver vincula=
do)</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"097096be171f">
<p local-id=3D"f0b0dbea03b4">A interface deve permitir navega=C3=A7=C3=A3o =
r=C3=A1pida para o plano correlato.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"3cb20daf-2c58-4264-b98a-96c6d71e27ca">
<h2 local-id=3D"2e8b26b34882" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-AdicionarPlanosCorrelatos">Adicionar Planos Correlatos</h=
2>
<p local-id=3D"3202edd25f7c">Dever=C3=A1 existir um bot=C3=A3o de a=C3=A7=
=C3=A3o:</p>
<p local-id=3D"d3b741ec935a"><strong>=E2=80=9CAdicionar Plano Correlato=E2=
=80=9D</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"c354ab7333d6">Ao clicar, o sistema dever=C3=A1 abrir um <str=
ong>modal de sele=C3=A7=C3=A3o de planos</strong> contendo:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"732a968a-ce5a-42c6-8629-559398e1defd">
<li local-id=3D"11f2ab95-03ed-42b5-93c5-c001f91de66f">
<p local-id=3D"469ddaa19d23">campo de <strong>busca por texto</strong></p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"8cd841a0-afa2-4fff-8b34-116d1e5ac0c3">
<p local-id=3D"7b8b155c1d1a">filtros para:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"dee09735-084f-4061-a5f1-7eadd11f0994">
<li local-id=3D"e407bc47-9e13-42d7-8e55-922432405e03">
<p local-id=3D"51e1f3c04073">status</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5682f058-76a7-47ff-b645-9f6833ba9ab2">
<p local-id=3D"1f0bf7f68218">respons=C3=A1vel</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ba0f6a4d-40db-4b0e-8d2c-d3f7c2ce0dc6">
<p local-id=3D"f40eaa73d19e">=C3=A1rea</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"94a998e2-50be-4749-b2b8-f370c06d1b80">
<p local-id=3D"f3f2b9236d9e">tags</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c56da7ea-b0a4-4502-b9ee-907d8e1cbb85">
<p local-id=3D"92a33d714a78">per=C3=ADodo</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"4374d099-39e4-44da-838e-38dc45c2a0d1">
<p local-id=3D"cd8da174f449">lista de resultados</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1c5eca7c-b89b-4730-aad1-7b3b813cf2e6">
<p local-id=3D"2a96add7de04">op=C3=A7=C3=A3o de associar <em>(imagem 1)</em=
></p>
<ul local-id=3D"06bcf6f30244">
<li local-id=3D"75920088ad72">
<p local-id=3D"22db80b9f4f9">Mensagem de confirma=C3=A7=C3=A3o para associa=
r</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"68005cfed061">
<p local-id=3D"a28fd3160ca6">op=C3=A7=C3=A3o de desassociar <em>(imagem 2)<=
/em></p>
<ul local-id=3D"d57d0711fdfb">
<li local-id=3D"8a3f44ae3847">
<p local-id=3D"d597a91c53fb">Mensagem de confirma=C3=A7=C3=A3o para desasso=
ciar <em>(imagem 3)</em></p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"2d3ac9ea80fd">A interface deve permitir selecionar <strong>u=
m ou mais planos</strong> e confirmar a vincula=C3=A7=C3=A3o.</p>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-not=
e">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-info=
rmation-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p local-id=3D"271a1002e2b1">Verificar a utiliza=C3=A7=C3=A3o do mesmo form=
ato da tela de Riscos =E2=86=92 indicadores que tem a funcionalidade de ass=
ociar, desassociar. Segue o comportamento sugerido abaixo:</p>
</div>
