<p local-id=3D"eafc61d35bf4"></p>
<hr local-id=3D"28d510c7-6fbf-4e86-a0f0-7decdc598c9f">
<h2 local-id=3D"4ba1b58d9fae" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-UsabilidadeePerformance">Usabilidade e Performance</h2>
<p local-id=3D"8b8a9ba47fbb">A interface deve considerar:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"f941ecf7-8c6a-495c-a92b-e6ddba7d312e">
<li local-id=3D"1e5a8424-c17c-4a70-bcf1-2e3181654072">
<p local-id=3D"196b685affab">suporte a grande volume de planos</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"63a4f16a-4806-47ec-9f2b-6596613aca65">
<p local-id=3D"32058931f898">carregamento paginado ou sob demanda</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1569c4d1-279e-4f4c-998a-e5ea9996c93b">
<p local-id=3D"7b282b2ab092">indica=C3=A7=C3=A3o visual clara dos planos j=
=C3=A1 correlacionados</p>
<ul local-id=3D"fd8c6b57d234">
<li local-id=3D"6bf0774de7b9">
<p local-id=3D"f883b96a725d">A=C3=A7=C3=A3o: mostrar os planos de a=C3=A7=
=C3=A3o associados/correlacionados</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"995e7706-90bc-42c8-9519-b877c3a3c108">
<h2 local-id=3D"758ee99a9379" id=3D"RQ005-PermitirRastreabilidadeentrePlano=
sdeA=C3=A7=C3=A3o-EstadosdaInterface">Estados da Interface</h2>
<p local-id=3D"8af8852c584e">O design deve prever os seguintes estados:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b5d7131d-4386-41c1-afcb-1467caef8740">
<li local-id=3D"f6adb500-1868-46f1-b13b-bc4372ec153c">
<p local-id=3D"c039b4e5c519">sem planos correlatos (informar mensagem: N=C3=
=A3o existem plano de a=C3=A7=C3=A3o correlacionados)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e7dc6b8f-c524-40c4-a5bb-af8236396a57">
<p local-id=3D"d3aace070a9d">carregando resultados (filtros)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"88e139c7-4e7d-489e-a10b-586048bec307">
<p local-id=3D"7873ec072b1f">lista com m=C3=BAltiplos correlatos (mostrar c=
orrelacionados)</p></li>
</ul>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
